FBIS4-64488 "drweu086_i_94005" FBIS-WEU-94-086 Daily Report 4 May 1994 FRANCE Malaysia's Mahathir Arrives for Private Visit Malaysia's Mahathir Arrives for Private Visit BK0405105094 Kuala Lumpur Voice of Malaysia in English 0600 GMT 4 May 94 BK0405105094 Kuala Lumpur Voice of Malaysia English BFN [Text] The prime minister, Datuk Sri Dr. Mahathir Mohamed, has arrived in Paris on a two-day private visit during which he will meet with his French counterpart, Edouard Balladur, and local business leaders. Through the (?MATRA) companies, France is competing with Canada to build an underground system in Kuala Lumpur. The prime minister leaves for the United States tomorrow.
